quran[159]{c,v,t}:
  7,88,"Mbatu mawnintiniingu e yimЙ“e makko Й“en wi'i : \"Ko maa men yaltine an Su'aybu, e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e wonndude e maaЙ—a ka saare amen, maa ruttoЙ—on e diina amen\". -O maaki : \"Hay si tawii ko men aГұuЙ“e [Й—um]"
  7,89,"GomЙ—ii (haray) men fefindike e hoore Alla fenaande si men ruttike e diina mon Й“aawo nde Alla daЙ—ndi men e makka. Alanaa men nde men ruttoo e makka si wanaa nde Alla Joomi amen muuyi. Joomi amen yaajanii kala huunde Anndal. Ko e Alla men fawii. Joomi amen, Гұaawir hakkunde amen e yimЙ“e amen Й“en goonga, ko An woni Й“urЙ—o moЖҙЖҙude e ГұaawooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,90,"Mbatu Й“en yedduЙ“e e yimЙ“e makko Й“en wi'i : \"Pellet, si on jokkii Su'aybu, onon ontuma ko on hayruЙ“e"
  7,91,"Dillaango ngon nanngi Й“e, Й“e waЙ—tini ka koЙ—ooli maЙ“Й“e ko Й“e jicciiЙ“e-Й—aanii"
  7,92,"ЖҒen fennunooЙ“e Su'aybu, (Й“e halkorino) wa si Й“e meeЙ—aa wuurude e ngon [hoЙ—o]. ЖҒen fennunooЙ“e Su'aybu, Й“e laatino kamЙ“e woni hayruЙ“e Й“en"
  7,93,"O Й—uurni Й“e, o maaki : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, gomЙ—ii mi yottinii e mo'on Nule Joomi am Й—en mi laaЙ“anii on (reedu). E ko honno mi surnortoo e yimЙ“e yedduЙ“e"
  7,94,"Men nulaali e saare hay e Annbaajo, si wanaa Men nanngirii yimЙ“e mayre Й“en saЙ—teende e lorra belajo'o, Й“e yankinoto"
  7,95,"Refti Men waЙ—titiri nokku bone on moЖҙЖҙere, haa Й“e Й—uuЙ—i, Й“e wi'i : \"GomЙ—ii saЙ—tteende e newennde heЙ“iino baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en\". Men nanngiri Й“e juhal, tawi kamЙ“e Й“e so'aa anndude"
  7,96,"Sinno yimЙ“e ca'e Й“en gomЙ—inno Й“e huli (Joomi maЙ“Й“e), Men udditanayno Й“e moЖҙЖҙereeji immorde ka Kammu e ka leydi. Kono Й“e fenni, Men nanngitiri Й“e (lepte Й—en) kon ko Й“e faggitotonoo"
  7,97,"Hara yimЙ“e ca'e Й“en hooli nde lepte Amen Й—en arataa Й“e jemma, hara hiЙ“e Й—aanii"
  7,98,"Kaa hara yimЙ“e ca'e Й“en hooli nde lepte Amen Й—en arataa Й“e ka walluhaa, hara hiЙ“e fija"
  7,99,E Й“e hooli pewje Alla Й—en? Hoolotaako pewje Alla Й—en si wanaa yimЙ“e hayruЙ“e Й“en
  7,100,"E Й“annganaali Й“en ronooЙ“e leydi Й“en Й“aawo (halkagol) yimЙ“e mayri Й“en, wonnde si Men Muuyuno Men meminirayno Й“e [lepte Й—en] junuubi maЙ“Й“e Й—in? Men nota e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en hara kamЙ“e Й“e nanataa"
  7,101,"ЖҠen ca'e, MeЙ—en fillano maa kumpite majje. GomЙ—ii NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en addanii Й“e Й“anngannduyeeji, Й“e wonaano gomЙ—inooЙ“e ko Й“e fenni kon ko adii. Ko wano nii All notirta e Й“erЙ—e heeferЙ“e Й“en"
  7,102,"Men tawaano ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e hunnooЙ“e ahadi ; si ko men tawi, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e ko faasiqiiЙ“e"
  7,103,"Refti Men Nulidi Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e Muusaa e Maandeeji Amen Й—in haa e Fir'awna e mbatu mu'un, Й“e yeddi Й—i. Ndaaru ko honno battane bonnooЙ“e Й“en laatornoo"
  7,104,"Muusaa maaki : \"Ko an yo Fir'awna, min ko NulaaЙ—o immorde ka JeyЙ—o Winndere nden"
  7,105,No hanndi e am nde mi wowlataa e hoore Alla si wanaa goonga. GomЙ—ii mi addanii on Й“anngannduyee immorde ka Joomi mon. neldam e Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en
  7,106,"[Fir'awna] wi'i : \"Si tawii a ardii e Maande, addu nde si tawii ko a jeyaaЙ—o e goonguЙ“e Й“en"
  7,107,"O werliiii tuggordu makko ndun, jaka ko ndu biidaande=ngoolwa Й“anngundi"
  7,108,"O yaltini junngo makko ngon, jaka yoo ko ngo rawnungo wonannde ndaarooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,109,"Mbatu yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“en wi'i : \"Pellet, oo, ko mbileejo annduЙ—o"
  7,110,"O faala yaltinnde on ka leydi mo'on\". -\"Ko honЙ—um yamirton"
  7,111,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"Nennu mo e musiЙ—Й—o makko on, nulaa e ca'e Й—en mooЙ“ooЙ“e (mbile)"
  7,112,ЖҒe addane kala mbileejo annduЙ—o
  7,113,"MbileeЙ“e Й“en ari Fir'awna Й“e wi'i : \"Hara njoЙ“di no woodani men, si men wonii fooluЙ“e Й“en"
  7,114,"O wi'i : \"Eyyo, haray on jeyaama e Й“aЙ—tinaaЙ“e Й“en"
  7,115,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"Ko an yo Muusaa, si Й—a yiЙ—i ko nde bugotoЙ—aa, maa men wona (adotooЙ“e) bugagol"
  7,116,"O maaki : \"Bugee\". Nde Й“e bugii, Й“e mbilЙ—ii gite yimЙ“e Й“en, Й“e hulЙ“ini Й“e, Й“e addi mbilewu mawnungu"
  7,117,"Men wahyini e Muusaa wonnde : \"Bugo tuggordu maa ndun\". Jaka yoo hindi moЙ—a ko Й“e fefindotonoo"
  7,118,"Goonga on feeГұi, ko Й“e gollaynoo kon [fow] boni"
  7,119,ЖҒe foolaa Й—on Й“e hooti ko Й“e jaasuЙ“e
  7,120,MbileeЙ“e Й“en suuyi sujji
  7,121,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"Men gomЙ—inii JeyЙ—o Winndere nden"
  7,122,JeyЙ—o Muusaa e Haaruuna
  7,123,"Fir'awna wi'i : \"On gomЙ—in mo ado mi duЕӢinannde=sakkitoore on? Pellet, Й—um Й—oo ko fewjoore nde fewjuЙ—on ka saare fii no yaltiniron ton yimЙ“e mayre. ma on anndonu"
  7,124,"Ma mi taЖҙa juuЙ—e mon Й—en e koyЙ—e mon Й—en (mi) luutindira, refti ma mi feta on denndaangal"
  7,125,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"Menen, ko faade ka Joomi amen woni ruttorde amen"
  7,126,"A aГұiraali men si wanaa fii men gomЙ—inii Maandeeji Joomi amen, tuma nde Й—i arunoo men. Joomi amen! Yuppu muГұal e amen, Жҙettitaa men ko men jebbilii Й“e"
  7,127,"Mbatu yimЙ“e Fir'awna ngun wi'i : \"A accay Muusaa e yimЙ“e mun Й“en no bonnira ka leydi, o acce an e reweteeЙ—i maa Й—in?!\" O wi'i : \"Ma men waru Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e worЙ“e Й“en men accita Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e rewЙ“e Й“en (wuura). Pellet, menen, e dow maЙ“Й“e ko men foolooЙ“e"
  7,128,"Muusaa maakani yimЙ“e makko Й“en : \"Wallinoree Alla muГұГұoЙ—on. Pellet, leydi ndin ka Alla woodani, Himo ronina ndi on Mo O muuyi e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. Battane moЖҙЖҙe Й—en ko gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en woodani"
  7,129,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"Men lorranooma ado a arde men e Й“aawo nde arЙ—aa men\". O maaki : \"Hino jortaa nde Joomi mon halkata gaГұo mon O lontina on ka leydi, O ndaara ko honno gollirton"
  7,130,"GomЙ—ii Men nanngirii yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“en kokke e Й—uytagol dimЙ—e ; belajo'o, Й“e waajitoto"
  7,131,"Si moЖҙЖҙere nden arii Й“e, Й“e wi'a : \"MeЙ—en hanndi e ndee Й—oo\" ; si bone on heЙ“ii Й“e, Й“e kiitinora Muusaa e wonnduЙ“e e makko Й“en. Anndee pellet, kiiti maЙ“Й“e Й—in ko ka Alla iwri, kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en anndaa"
  7,132,"ЖҒe wi'i : \"Kala ko addan Й—aa Й“en e Aayaa fii no mbilЙ—oraa men Й—um ; men wonaali gomЙ—inooЙ“e ma"
  7,133,"Men wurti e maЙ“Й“e waame, e kanu, e karan=tendi, e totiiji=paabi, e ЖҙiiЖҙam, ko Aayeeje fensitaaЙ—e, Й“e mawnintinii, Й“e laatii yimЙ“e bomЙ“e"
  7,134,"Tuma nde lepte Й—en yanunoo e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e wi'i : \"ko an Muusaa, torano men Joomi maa sabu kon ko O ahodi e maaЙ—a. Si a huncanii men Й—ee lepte, ma men gomЙ—ine, ma men accide kadi e Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en"
  7,135,"Nde Men huncannoo Й“e lepte Й—en haa e lajal ngal Й“e yottotoo, jaka yoo kamЙ“e ko Й“e firtooЙ“e (ahadi maЙ“Й“e ndin)"
  7,136,"Men yottii e maЙ“Й“e ; Men yooliri Й“e ka maayo sabu ko Й“e fenniri kon Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Й“e laatii welsindiiЙ“e e majje"
  7,137,"Men ronini yimЙ“e wonanooЙ“e lo'ineede Й“en fuЙ—naange leydi ndin e hiirnaange mayri ndi Men barkini e mu'un. Konngol Joomi maa moЖҙЖҙongol ngol timmii e Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en sabu ko Й“e muГұГұinoo kon. Men halki ko Fir'awna e yimЙ“e mun Й“en moЖҙЖҙinanynoo, e kon ko Й“e Й“amtaynoo (e kuЙ“eeje)"
  7,138,"Men lummbini Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en maayo ngon, Й“e rewi ka yimЙ“e ГұiiЙ“uЙ“e (e rewugol) sanamuuji mu'un, Й“e wi'i : \"Ko an yo Muusaa, waЙ—an men reweteeЙ—o wano reweteeЙ—i woodirani Й“e non\". O maaki : \"Pellet, onon ko on yimЙ“e majjooЙ“e"
  7,139,"Pellet, Й“ee Й—oo, ko Й“e woni e mun kon ko halkaaЙ—um, kadi ko mere woni ko Й“e gollaynoo"
  7,140,"E ko ko woori Alla mi Й—aЙ“Й“anta on reweteeЙ—o, Kanko O Й“urnii on e Winndere nden"
  7,141,"(Annditee) tuma nde Men daЙ—ndunoo on e yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“en, hiЙ“e meeЙ—ina on lepte bonЙ—e : Й“e wara Й“iЙ—Й“e mon worЙ“e Й“e heddina rewЙ“e mon Й“en. No e Й—um mooЙ—on jarrabuyee mawЙ—o immorde ka Joomi mon"
  7,142,"Men haldidi e Muusaa jemmaaji cappanЙ—i tati, Men timminiri Й—i sappo, happu Joomi makko on timmiri jemmaaji cappanЙ—e nayi. Muusaa maakani neene-gooto makko on Haaruuna : \"Lonto lam ka yimЙ“e am, moЖҙЖҙinaa (fiyaake maЙ“Й“e), wata a jokku laawol bonnooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,143,"Nde Muusaa arunoo fii happu amen on Joomi makko yewti mo, o maaki : \"Joomi, hollam mi ndaare!\" O Daali : \"A yi'ataa lam ; kono ndaaru fello ngon : si ngo ГұiiЙ“ii e nokku maggo, aray ka yi'aa lam\". Nde Joomi makko feeГұannoo fello ngon, O waЙ—ti ngo Й—iggu ngo, Muusaa yani faЙ—Й—aa. Nde o Й—iwtunoo, o maaki : \"Senayee woodanu Ma! Mi tuubanii Ma, min ko mi arano e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  7,144,"O Daali : \"Ko an yo Muusaa, Min Mi suЙ“orii ma e yimЙ“e Й“en Nule Am Й—en e konngol am ngol. Jogito ko Mi jonnu maa kon jeyeeЙ—aa e yettooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,145,"Men winndani mo ka alluuje kala huunde, waaju e fensitannde kala huunde. Jogitor nde doole, yamiraa yimЙ“e maa Й“en jogitagol ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e mayre. Arma Mi holla on galle faasiqiiЙ“e Й“en"
  7,146,"Mi suray gaay e Aayeeje Am Й—en Й“en mawnintinorayЙ“e ka leydi ko aldaa e goonga. Hay si Й“e yi'i kala Aaya Й“e gomЙ—intaa mo, si Й“e yi'ii laawol peewal ngol Й“e jogitotaako ngol laawol, si Й“e yi'ii laawol bewre ngol Й“e jogitoo ngol laawol. ЖҠum non, ko tawde Й“e fennii Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Й“e woni welsindiiЙ“e e majje"
  7,147,"ЖҒen fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en e hawrugol e laakara, golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en bonii. Hara Й“en yoЙ“oyte si wanaa kon ko Й“e gollaynoo"
  7,148,"YimЙ“e Muusa Й“en jogitii Й“aawo makko cuЙ—aari maЙ“Й“e ndin ngaari Й“anndinnke, hindi mari nuunaango=kuunaali. E Й“e yi'aali wonnde nde yewtidataa e maЙ“Й“e ndi fewntanaa Й“e kadi e laawol? ЖҒe jogitike ndii [ngaari reweteendi], Й“e laatii tooГұooЙ“e"
  7,149,"Nde yantunoo e juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e yi'i wonnde gomЙ—ii Й“e majjii, Й“e wi'i : \"Si Joomi amen yurmaaka men, O haforani men, pellet, men laatoday e hayruЙ“e Й“en"
  7,150,"Nde Muusaa ruttinoo e yimЙ“e makko Й“en ko o tikkuЙ—o, suniiЙ—o, o maaki : \"Bonii kon ko lontiЙ—on lam Й“aawo am. E on hawjan yamiroore Joomi mon nden?!\" O weddii alluuje Й—en o nanngi hoore neene-gooto makko on himo pooЙ—a mo e makko. [Haaruuna] Maaki : \"Ko an yo Й“iЙ—Й—o neene am, Й“ee yimЙ“e lo'inii lam, Й“e do'i warugol lam. Wata a weltin ayЙ“e am, wata a waЙ—tidam kadi e yimЙ“e toonoЙ“e Й“en"
  7,151,"O maaki : \"Joomi am, haforanam min e neene-gooto am on, naadaa men ka yurmeende Maa. Ko An woni Й“urЙ—o yurmeede e yurmeteeЙ“e Й“en"
  7,152,"Pellet, Й“en jogitii Й“e ngaari ndin (reweteendi), arma tikkere heЙ“a Й“e immorde e Joomi maЙ“Й“e, e koyeera ka nguurndam aduna. Ko wano non Men yoЙ“irta fefindotooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,153,"ЖҒen golluЙ“e boneeji, refti Й“e tuubi Й“aawo Й—um Й“e gomЙ—ini, pellet, Joomi maa, Й“aawo Й—um, ko haforoowo, hinnotooЙ—o"
  7,154,"Nde tikkere nden deeЖҙunoo e Muusaa, o Жҙetti alluuje Й—en. Tawi no e binndoodi majje, peewal e yurmeende wonannde Й“en hulooЙ“e Joomi mun"
  7,155,"Muusaa suЙ“ii e yimЙ“e makko Й“en worЙ“e cappanЙ—e jeeЙ—iЙ—o fii happu Amen. Nde dillaango ngon nanngunoo Й“e, o maaki : \"Joomi, si a muuyuno, A halkayno Й“e ado hannde, e min kadi. E A halkiray men ko Й—ayЙ“e amen Й“en huuwi? ЖҠum wonaali si wanaa jarrabuyee MaaЙ—a, HiЙ—a majjinira Й—um on Mo muuyu-ЖҠaa, HiЙ—a fewna on Mo muuyu-ЖҠaa. Ko An woni giЙ—o Amen, haforan men yurme-ЖҠaa men. Ko An woni Й“urЙ—o moЖҙЖҙude e haforooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,156,"Winndanaa men ka aduna Й—oo moЖҙЖҙere, e ka laakara. Menen men tuubanii Ma. O Daali : \"Lepte Am Й—en, Mi meminay Й—e on mo Mi muuyi. Yurmeende Am nden yaajanii kala huunde. Arma Mi winndana nde Й“en hulooЙ“e (Alla), Й“e totta zakka, e Й“en gomЙ—inooЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en"
  7,157,"ЖҒen jokkayЙ“e NulaaЙ—o on, Annabaajo humammbinneejo, on mo Й“e tawta fii mun no winndaa ka maЙ“Й“e ka Tawreeta e ka Linnjiila. Himo yamira Й“e moЖҙЖҙere, o haЙ—a Й“e ЕӢiГұere, himo daginana Й“e dagiiЙ—i Й—in, o harminana Й“e soЙ“uЙ—i Й—in, o ittana Й“e teddeelo e kolommbooje=tonngi wonunooЙ—e e hoore-maЙ“Й“e. ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e mo, Й“e teddini mo, Й“e walli mo, Й“e jokki annoora JippinaaЙ—o wonndude e makko ; Й“en, ko kamЙ“e woni malaaЙ“e Й“en"
  7,158,"Maaku : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, min ko mi NulaaЙ—o Alla e mooЙ—on on denndaangal, On Mo woodani Й—um laamu kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. ReweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa kanko. Himo wuurna wara. GomЙ—inee Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko Annabaajo humammbinneejo on, on gomЙ—inЙ—o Alla e KonnguЙ—i Makko Й—in. Jokkee mo, belajo'o, on feeway"
  7,159,"Hino e yimЙ“e Muusaa Й“en, mofte fewnirayЙ—e (yimЙ“e Й“en) e goonga, ko Й—um woni ko Й“e nunЙ—irta"
  7,160,"Men senndi Й“e gori sappo e Й—iЙ—i mofte. Men wahyini e Muusaa tuma nde yimЙ“e makko Й“en Й—aЙ“Й“irnoo mo yarnineede wonnde : \"Piyir tuggordu maa ndun hayre nden\". ЖҒulli sappo e Й—iЙ—i yallti e mayre. GomЙ—ii gorol kala andii yariride mu'un. Men Й—owdinirani Й“e duule, Men Jippini e maЙ“Й“e demmbe-njuuri, e teewu colli. \"Г‘aamee e laaЙ“uЙ—i Й—i Men arsiki on\". ЖҒe tooГұaali Men, kono ko wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й“e tooГұaynoo"
  7,161,"Tuma nde Й“e wi'anaa : \"HoЙ—ee e ndee saare, Гұaamon e mayre nokku kala ka yiЙ—uЙ—on, wi'on : Й“oran men [goopi amen], naatiron ka damal ko on sujjuЙ“e, Men haforanay on goopi mon. Arma Men Й“eydana moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e Й“en"
  7,162,"TooГұuЙ“e Й“en e maЙ“Й“e wayliri konngol ngol ko wanaa ngol ngol Й“e wi'ananoo. Min Jippini e maЙ“Й“e lepte immorde ka kammu, sabu ko Й“e laatinoo hiЙ“e tooГұa"
  7,163,"Lanndo Й“e fii saare wonunoonde nden ka sera maayo, tuma nde Й“e jaggitaynoo e Aseweere nden, tuma nde liЖҙЖҙi maЙ“Й“e Й—in araynooЙ“e Гұalnde Aseweere maЙ“Й“e nden ko Й—i hummbuЙ—i, Гұalnde woni wanaa aseweere maЙ“Й“e Й—i arataa Й“e. Ko wano nii Men jarriborta Й“e kon ko Й“e faasonqinoraynoo"
  7,164,"Tuma nde jamaa jeyaaЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e wi'unoo : \"Ko honЙ—um waajoantoЙ—on yimЙ“e, Allaahu ko halkoowo Й“e maa O lepta Й“e lepte sattuЙ—e?\" ЖҒe wi'i : \"Ko [ittugol] nganto faade ka Joomi mo'on ; e belajo'o, kamЙ“e Й“e rentoto"
  7,165,"Nde Й“e yejjitunoo ko Й“e waajanoo fii mun kon, Men daЙ—ndi Й“en haЙ—aynooЙ“e e bone on, Men nanngiri Й“en tooГұuЙ“e lepte sattuЙ—e sabu ko Й“e faasonqinoraynoo"
  7,166,"Nde Й“e townitaninoo e ko Й“e haЙ—aa e mun kon, Men wi'ani Й“e : \"Laatee baaЙ—i jaasuЙ—i"
  7,167,"Janto tuma nde Joomi maa anndinnoo (wonnde) ma O Nulu e maЙ“Й“e haa Г‘alnde Darngal on meeЙ—inoowo Й“e lepte bonЙ—e. Pellet, Joomi maa ko yaawuЙ—e lepte, pellet kadi, ko O haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  7,168,"Men senndiri Й“e ka leydi jamaaji : hino e maЙ“Й“e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e, hino e maЙ“Й“e ko jaasi Й—um. Men jarribori Й“e moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i e bonЙ—i, belajo'o, kamЙ“e Й“e ruttoto"
  7,169,"Lontii Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e lontii Й“e (bomЙ“e), Й“e roni Deftere nden, hiЙ“e Жҙetta weeЙ“itanЙ—e oo aduna Й“e wi'a : \"Aray men haforanee\". Si weeЙ“itannde sugu mun arii e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e Жҙetta Й—um. Hara ahadi Deftere nden Жҙettidaaka e maЙ“Й“e, wonnde wata Й“e wowlu e Alla si wanaa goonga?! ЖҒe janngi ko woni e mayre. Ko galle laakara Й—en Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde Й“en rentiiЙ“e. E on haqqiltaa"
  7,170,"ЖҒen jogitotooЙ“e Deftere nden Й“e Гұinna julde, pellet, Menen Men yeebataa njoЙ“di moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,171,"Janto tuma nde Men Й“orunoo fello ngon senngo dow maЙ“Й“e, a sikkay ko ngo Й—owdi.ЖҒe felliti ngo yanat e maЙ“Й“e. \"Jogitoree ko Men okki on kon doole, jantee ko woni e mayre, belajo'o, on kulon Alla"
  7,172,"Janto kadi nde Joomi maa Жҙettunoo e Й“iЙ—Й“e Aadama Й“en ka keeci maЙ“Й“e jurriiyaaji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, O seendintini Й“e e wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in : \"Wanaa kon Min woni Joomi mon?\" ЖҒe wi'i : \"Ko non woniri, men seedike\". Ko fii (wata) on wi'oy Г‘alnde Darngal : \"Menen men woniino welsindiiЙ“e e Й—um Й—oo"
  7,173,"Maa wi'oyon : \"Anndee ko baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en sirkunoo ko adii, men wonti (tun) jurriiya Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e. E A halkiray men ko bonnooЙ“e Й“en waЙ—i"
  7,174,"Ko wano nii Men fensitirta Aayeeje Й—en, e belajo'o kamЙ“e Й“e ruttoto"
  7,175,"Janngan Й“e kumpite on mo Men okki Aayeeje Amen Й—en, o Й“oorii Й—e, seytaane jokki mo, e laatodii e majjuЙ“e Й“en"
  7,176,"Sinno Men muuyuno, Men Й“amtirayno mo Й—e, ko woni tun o heddike ka leydi o jokki mbeleeЙ—e makko. Sugu makko ko sifa rawaandu, si a ronndii ndu ndu lahay, maa si a terti ndu du lahay. Ko Й—um woni misal yimЙ“e fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en. Fillo qissaaji Й—in ; belajo'o, Й“e miijitoto"
  7,177,"[Alaa ko Й“uri] bonnde misal Й“en yimЙ“e fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, ko wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e woni ko Й“e tooГұaynoo"
  7,178,"Kala mo Alla fewni, ko on feewata ; kala kadi mo O majjini, ko Й“en hayruЙ“e Й“en"
  7,179,"GomЙ—ii Men taganii Jahannama ko Й—uuЙ—i e jinna e yimЙ“e. HiЙ“e mari Й“erЙ—e, Й“e faamirtaa Й—e. HiЙ“e mari gite, Й“e yi'irtaa Й—e. HiЙ“e mari noppi, Й“e nanirtaa Й—i. ЖҒen no wa'i wa neemoraaЙ—i, toode ko kamЙ“e Й“uri majjude. Ko Й“en woni welsindiiЙ“e Й“en"
  7,180,"Ko Alla woodani inЙ—e Й“urЙ—e moЖҙЖҙude Й—en. Noddiree Mo Й—e, tertoЙ—on Й“en ooГұotooЙ“e ka inЙ—e Makko : arma Й“e yoЙ“oyee ko Й“e gollaynoo"
  7,181,"Hino e Й“en Й“e Men tagi, mofte feewirayЙ—e goonga, ko Й—um kadi Й“e nunЙ—irta"
  7,182,"ЖҒen fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Men suyniray Й“e e nokku ka Й“e anndaa"
  7,183,"MiЙ—o nennana Й“e, pellet, pewje Am Й—en ko tiiЙ—uЙ—e"
  7,184,"E Й“ee miijitaaki? wonndiiЙ—o maЙ“Й“e on aldaa e jinna : on wonaali si wanaa jertinoowo Й“annguЙ—o"
  7,185,"E Й“e ndaaraali laamuuji kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, e ko Alla tagi e piiji, e haawnaaki hara lajal maЙ“Й“e ngal Й“adike? E ko yewtere honnde Й“aawo ndee Й—oo Й“e gomЙ—inta"
  7,186,"Kala mo Alla majjini, fewnoowo mo alaa. Himo acca Й“e e bewre maЙ“Й“e hiЙ“e bumam-bumannoo"
  7,187,"HiЙ“e lanndo maa fii darngal : \"ko honnde woni daragol maggal?\" Maaku : \"Anndee ganndal mun ko ka Joomi am woni. Alaa feГұГұioowo waqtu maggal on si wanaa Kanko. Ngal teddii ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Ngal arataa e mon si wanaa e juhal\". HiЙ“e lanndo maa a sikkay ko a huЙ“indiiЙ—o e Й—um. Maaku : \"Anndee ganndal mun ko ka Alla woni\". kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en anndaa [Й—um]"
  7,188,"Maaku : \"Mi waawanaa hoore-am nafa wanaa lorra, si wanaa ko Alla muuyi. Sinno miЙ—o anndunoo ko wirnii, mi hebbinorayno moЖҙЖҙere, bone kadi memataano lam. Mi wonaali si wanaa jertinoowo e wewlinoowo, wonannde yimЙ“e gomЙ—inooЙ“e"
  7,189,"Ko Kanko woni taguЙ—o on immorde e wonkii wooti, O waЙ—i e makki genndo makko, fii yo o deeЖҙu e makko. Tuma nde o renndunoo e makko, o sowii sowannde hoyfunde, o duumodi e mun. Nde o teddidunoo [e reedu ndun], Й“e torodi Alla Joomi maЙ“Й“e : \"Pellet, si a yeЙ—ii men (Й“iЙ—Й—o) yottiiЙ—o, ma men jeye e yettooЙ“e Ma Й“en"
  7,190,"Nde O yeЙ—unoo Й“e (Й“iЙ—Й—o) yottiiЙ—o, Й“e waЙ—idani Mo kafidiiЙ“e e kon ko O yeЙ—i Й“e. Alla toowii e kon ko Й“e sirkata"
  7,191,"E Й“e kafiday (Mo) e kon ko tagataa hay e huunde, kamЙ“e tigi ko Й“e tagaaЙ“e"
  7,192,"ЖҠi waawanaa Й“e ballal, wanaa (hay) ko'e majji Й—i wallata"
  7,193,"Si on noddii Й—i e peewal, Й—i jokkataa on. Hino fotanan on ter, si on noddii Й—i maa hara ko on deyЖҙuЙ“e"
  7,194,"Pellet, Й—in Й—i noddoton gaanin Alla, ko jeyaaЙ—i yeruuji mon. Noddee Й—i, yo Й—i jaabinanii on, si on laatike goonguЙ“e"
  7,195,"Hara hiЙ—i mari koyЙ—e ko Й—i yahra? kaa hiЙ—i mari juuЙ—e ko Й—i duГұira? Kaa hiЙ—i mari gite ko Й—i yi'ira? Kaa hiЙ—i mari noppi ko Й—i nanira? Maaku : \"Noddee kafidiiЙ—i mon Й—in, refti fewjanon lam, wata on nennitanam"
  7,196,"Pellet, ko Alla woni heftuЙ—o e am on, On JippinЙ—o Deftetere nden, ko Kanko woni heftoowo moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en"
  7,197,"ЖҠin Й—i noddoton gaanin Mo, Й—i hattanaa e wallugol on, wanaa kadi ko'e majji Й—i wallata"
  7,198,"Si on noddii Й—i e peewal, Й—i nanataa. A yi'ay Й—i hiЙ—i ndaare, (kono) kannji Й—i yi'ataa"
  7,199,"Jogito yaafuyee, yamiraa moЖҙЖҙere nden Й—uurno-Й—aa e majjuЙ“e Й“en"
  7,200,"Si sowinsinoore arii heЙ“ude ma immorde e seytaane, moolor Alla. Kanko ko O nanoowo, annduЙ—o"
  7,201,"Pellet, Й“en gomЙ—uЙ“e, si sowonsinoore heЙ“ii Й“e immorde e sytaane, Й“e annditay [Alla] : jaka yoo kamЙ“e ko Й“e yi'ooЙ“e"
  7,202,"SiЙ“Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en [ka yimЙ“e] hino pooЙ—a Й“e e bewre, refti Й“e raЙ“Й“indintaako"
  7,203,"Si a addanaali Й“e Aaya, Й“e wi'ay : \"Ko haЙ—unoo sincaa Й—um?\" Maaku : \"Anndee ko jokku-mi, ko kon wahyina e am immorde ka Joomi am. Ndee Й—oo [Alqur'aanaare] ko hujjaaji (Й“annguЙ—i) immorde ka Joomi mon, e peewal e yurmeende wonnande yimЙ“e gomЙ—inooЙ“e"
  7,204,"Si Alqur'aana no janngeede, heЙ—tee nde deЖҙЖҙiton ; belajo'o, on yurminte"
  7,205,"Annditu Joomi maaЙ—a ka wonkii maa, ka yankinaare e ka kulol, ko aldaa e feГұГұingol konngol, bimmbi e kiikiiЙ—e, wata a laatodo e welsindiiЙ“e Й“en"
  7,206,"Pellet, Й“en [Malaa'ikaaЙ“e] wonЙ“e ka Joomi maa, Й“e townitantaako rewugol Mo, hiЙ“e subbunhinanoo Mo, ko Kanko woni ko Й“e sujjanta"
  8,1,"HiЙ“e lanndo maa fii konhoyri. Maaku : \"Konhoyri ndin ko Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on jeyi\". Hulee Alla, moЖҙЖҙinon hakkunde mon Й—oftoЙ—on kadi Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on si on laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  8,2,"Pellet, gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, ko Й“en Й“e (tawata) si Alla jantaama, Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en hulay. Si Aayeeje Makko Й—en janngaama e maЙ“Й“e, Й—e Й“eyda Й“e gomЙ—inal. Ko e Joomi maЙ“Й“e (tun) Й“e fawotoo"
  8,3,ЖҒen ГұinnooЙ“e julde nden e kon ko Men arsiki Й“e hiЙ“e wintoo=nafqa
  8,4,"ЖҒen Й—on, ko kamЙ“e woni gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en ka goonga : hino woodani Й“e darjaaji ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e, e haforaneede e arsike tedduЙ—o"
  8,5,"Ko wano Joomi maa yaltinirno maa non ka suudu maa sabu goonga, (tawi non) pellet, fedde e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en ko aГұuЙ“e (Й—um)"
  8,6,HiЙ“e wennja maa fii goonga kan Й“aawo nde ka feeГұi ; a sikkay ko Й“e wonaaЙ“e soggeede e maayde hara kamЙ“e hiЙ“e ndaara (Й—um)
  8,7,"(Jantee) tuma nde Alla fodunoo on gootel e feddeeji Й—in Й—iЙ—i, wonnde \"gootel e majji ko onon woodani, hiЙ—on yeloo sinno ko fedde nde alaa doole nden laatantoo on, (tawi) Alla no yiЙ—i nde O goonginirta goonga kan Daaluyeeji Makko Й—in O taЖҙa Й“abbe heeferaaЙ“e Й“en"
  8,8,"Fii yo O goonginiri goonga kan O bonne fii meere nden, hay si bomЙ“e Й“en yiЙ—aa"
  8,9,"(Jantee) tuma nde faabinoranoЙ—on Joomi mon O jaabinani on : \"Min ko Mi Й“eydiroowo on ujunere e Malaa'ika jokkondirooЙ“e"
  8,10,"Alla waЙ—iraali Й—um si wanaa welo-welo e fii no Й“erЙ—e mon deeЖҙira Й—um. Balla wonaali si wanaa immorde ka Alla. Pellet, Alla ko FooluЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  8,11,"E Tuma nde ЕӢoЕӢre nden hippaynoo on hoolaare immorde ka Makko, Himo Jippinana on ndiyam immorde ka kammu fii yo O laЙ“Й“inir on Й—am, O ittana on soЙ“e seytaane, e fii yo O tiiЙ—inir (Й—um) e Й“erЙ—e mon O tabintinira Й—am teppe [mon] Й—en"
  8,12,"Tuma nde Joomi maa wahyinaynoo e Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“e : \"Min MiЙ—o wonndi e mo'on : tabintinee gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en. Arma Mi bugoo Й—enЖҙere e Й“erЙ—e heeferЙ“e Й“en. Tappee dow daaЙ—e Й—en tappon e maЙ“Й“e kala wunnjere"
  8,13,"ЖҠum, ko fii kamЙ“e Й“e lunndike Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on. \"Kala non lunndiiЙ—o Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, pellet, Alla ko saЙ—tuЙ—o lepte"
  8,14,"ЖҠum mooЙ—on ; meeЙ—ee Й—um ! E wonnde pellet, no waadani heeferЙ“e Й“en lepte Yiite"
  8,15,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, si on hawrii e Й“en heeferЙ“e ko Й“e mooЙ“iiЙ“e, wata on huccintinan Й“e Й“abbe Й—en"
  8,16,"Kala hunccintinЙ—o Й“e nden Гұalnde (Й“abbal mu'un), -si wanaa hara ko on heЙ“Й“itantooЙ—o hare nden, maa hara ko ukkitotooЙ—o e fedde, -gomЙ—ii haray o ruttodii e tikkere immorde ka Alla, jaaЖҙorde maЙ“Й“e nden ko Jahannama nge bonii ruttorde"
  8,17,"On waraano Й“e : Ko Allaahu On wari Й“e. A feranooki tuma ferinoЙ—aa : Ko Allaahu On ferii, e fii yo O jarribor gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en immorde ka Makko jarrabuyee moЖҙЖҙuЙ—o. Pellet, Alla ko Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o"
  8,18,"ЖҠum mooЙ—on, ko tawde pellet, Alla ko lo'inoowo pewje heeferЙ“e Й“en"
  8,19,"Si on Й—aЙ“Й“ii uddital, gomЙ—ii uddital arii on. Si on haЙ—itike, ko Й—um Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on. Si on fillitike, Men fillitoo. Fedde mon nden duncanoytaa on hay e huunde, hay si nde Й—uuЙ—ii. Tawde pellet, Alla no wonndi e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  8,20,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, Й—oftee Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on wata on huccu mo hara hiЙ—on nannde (Aayeeje Й—en)"
  8,21,"Wata on wa'u wa Й“en wi'unooЙ“e : \"Men nanii\", tawi kamЙ“e Й“e alaa e nanude"
  8,22,"Pellet, ko Й“uri bonnde e ko ruugata kon ka Alla, ko faaЙ—uЙ“e mumЙ“e Й“e haqqiltaa"
  8,23,"Sinno Alla annduno e maЙ“Й“e moЖҙЖҙere, O naninayno Й“e. Hay si O naninno Й“e, Й“e huccitayno hara ko Й“e Й—uurnii Й“e"
  8,24,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, Nootee Alla e NulaaЙ—o on si Й“e noddii on fi ko wuurnata on (e goonga), anndee pellet, Alla no heeda hakkunde neЙ—Й—o e Й“ernde mun, e wonnde pellet, ko ka Makko mooЙ“oyteЙ—on"
  8,25,"Rentee e bone tawЙ—o o memataa tooГұuЙ“e Й“en e mooЙ—on tun. Anndee pellet, Alla ko saЙ—tuЙ—o lepte"
  8,26,"Annditee tuma wonunoЙ—on fanЙ—uЙ“e, lo'inaaЙ“e ka leydi, hiЙ—on hula nde yimЙ“e Й“en jilotoo on. O weerni on, O semmbiniri on ballal Makko ngal, O arsiki on immorde e laaЙ“uЙ—i belajo'o, on yettay (neemaaji makko Й—in)"
  8,27,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, wata on janfo Alla e NulaaЙ—o on, janfoЙ—on koolaaje mon Й—en hara hiЙ—on anndi"
  8,28,"Anndee pellet, jawle mon Й—en e Й“iЙ—Й“e mon Й“en ko fitina e wonnde no ka Alla njoЙ“di mawndi"
  8,29,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, si on hulii Alla, O waЙ—anay on senndindirЙ—um (goonga e meere), O heefana on bakkatuuji mon O haforana on. Alla ko Jom-ЖҒural mawnungal"
  8,30,"(Jantii) tuma nde heeferЙ“e Й“en fewjanayno maa fii yoЙ“e aamin maa Й“e ware maa Й“e yaltine. HiЙ“e fewja, Alla no fewja. Ko Alla Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude fewjooЙ“e Й“en"
  8,31,"Si Aayeeje Amen Й—en janngaama e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e wi'a : \"GomЙ—ii men nanii, sinno men yiЙ—uno men wowlayno yeru Й—um, ndee wonaali si wanaa tinndi adinooЙ“e"
  8,32,"E tuma Й“e wi'unoo : \"Yaa Alla, si tawii ko Й—um woni goonga immorde ka MaaЙ—a, haray saaЖҙin kaaЖҙe e amen immorde ka kammu, maa addanaa men lepte muusuЙ—e"
  8,33,"Alla wonaani leptoowo Й“e, hara an hiЙ—a hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Alla siforaali leptoowo Й“e, hara kamЙ“e hiЙ“e insinaade"
  8,34,"Ko haЙ—ata Й“e nde Alla leptataa Й“e, hara kamЙ“e hiЙ“e sakkaade Juulirde hormante nden? ЖҒe wonaali heftuЙ“e nde. HeftuЙ“e Mo wonaali si wanaa Й“en gomЙ—umЙ“e, kono Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e anndaa"
  8,35,"Julde maЙ“Й“e nden ka Suudu wonaali, si wanaa wuuЙ—ugol e kellugol : \"MeeЙ—iree lepte Й—en sabu ko yeddiraynoЙ—on kon"
  8,36,"Pellet, Й“en yedduЙ“e, hiЙ“e nafqira jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en no Й“e sakkora (yimЙ“e Й“en) e laawol Alla ngol. Maa Й“e nafqu Й—e, refti wontana Й“e ninse, refti Й“e foolee. ЖҒen yedduЙ“e non, ko ka Jahannama Й“e mooЙ“oytee"
  8,37,"Fii yo Alla senndindir soЙ“e Й—en e ko laaЙ“i kon, O waЙ—a soЙ“e Й—en yoga mun e dow yoga, O fawindira Й—um fow O waЙ—ta Й—um ka nder Jahamma. ko Й“en Й—on woni hayruЙ“e Й“en"
  8,38,"Maakan Й“en yedduЙ“e: si Й“e haЙ—itike; Й“e haforante ko yawti. Si Й“e fillitike, haray gomЙ—ii laawol adinooЙ“e Й“en yawtii"
  8,39,"HaЙ“ee Й“e haa ka tawata fitina laatotaako, diina kan fow laatanoo Alla. Si Й“e haЙ—itike, haray pellet, Alla ko reenuЙ—o ko Й“e golla kon"
  8,40,"Si Й“e huccitii, anndee pellet, ko Alla woni GiЙ—o mon. O yooЙ—ii GiЙ—o O yooЙ—ii Ballo"